IC_Poisson <- function(x) {
 upper = mean(x) + 1.96 * sqrt(mean(x)/length(x))
 lower = mean(x) - 2.58 * sqrt(mean(x)/length(x))
 ci <- c(lower, upper)
 return(ci)
 }
